Entropy‑rate scheduling:

Inside ignition band β ∈ [0.3934, 0.3990], use full schedule;

Outside, throttle by a factor g(β) defined from C(β)/β = |S'(β)|.

2.2 Heat‑bath (Glauber) variant
Conditional probability for s_i=1:

